            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "## Weather-Driven Retail Demand Intelligence\n",
                "\n",
                "**Business Impact:** This dashboard transforms real-time weather data into actionable retail intelligence, enabling proactive inventory management, optimized staffing, and category-specific merchandising decisions.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Key Capabilities:**\n",
                "* **Predictive Staffing:** Identifies stores requiring increased staff based on weather-driven demand signals (AC cooling, rain gear, outdoor events)\n",
                "* **Regional Intelligence:** Compare demand patterns across West, Mountain, South, Midwest, and Northeast regions\n",
                "* **Historical Validation:** Proves continuous pipeline operation with time-series temperature tracking\n",
                "* **Operational Efficiency:** Morning operations view provides at-a-glance city-level demand signals\n",
                "\n",
                "**ROI Drivers:** Reduced stockouts during weather events, optimized labor costs, improved customer satisfaction through better product availability, and data-driven category focus alignment.\n",
                "\n",
                "*Use the Region filter above to drill into specific geographic areas.*"
              ]
